| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
+---------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | BytesProcessedNode                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |   Federated                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |  Limit: skip=0, fetch=10                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |
|               |   Sort: u DESC NULLS FIRST                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
|               |     Projection: hits.MobilePhone, hits.MobilePhoneModel, count(DISTINCT hits.UserID) AS u                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
|               |       Aggregate: groupBy=[[hits.MobilePhone, hits.MobilePhoneModel]], aggr=[[count(DISTINCT hits.UserID)]]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
|               |         TableScan: hits projection=[UserID, MobilePhone, MobilePhoneModel], full_filters=[hits.MobilePhoneModel != Utf8("")]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
| physical_plan | BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |   SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
|               |     CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
|               |       VirtualExecutionPlan name=postgres compute_context=host=Tcp("benchmarking-postgres-rw.dataplatform.svc.cluster.local"),port=5432,db=clickbench_accelerated,user=postgres, initial_sql=SELECT "hits"."MobilePhone", "hits"."MobilePhoneModel", count(DISTINCT "hits"."UserID") AS "u" FROM "hits" WHERE ("hits"."MobilePhoneModel" <> '') GROUP BY "hits"."MobilePhone", "hits"."MobilePhoneModel" ORDER BY "u" DESC NULLS FIRST LIMIT 10 |
|               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
